overview: Horror - When college students Brooke and A.J. set out to make a documentary on six missing kids, rumored to be the victims of a deadly curse, they have no idea of the danger they're walking into. While digging for answers, Brooke and A.J. stir the emotions of the mysterious locals and uncover a world of dark secrets and unspeakable evil.
title: Skinwalker: Curse of the Shaman
